☕ Coffee Sales Analysis Dashboard Project Report
📊 A professional Excel dashboard project based on the Kaggle Coffee Sales dataset.

📖 Executive Summary
This project transforms raw coffee sales data into an interactive dashboard using Pivot Tables, Pivot Charts, KPI Cards, and Slicers to support data-driven business decisions.
🎯 Problem Statement
Businesses often struggle to extract meaningful insights from raw transactional data. This dashboard provides a single interactive view for monitoring sales performance.
🎯 Business Objectives
✅ Track Total Revenue
✅ Identify Best-Selling Coffee
✅ Analyze Sales Trends
✅ Compare Payment Methods
✅ Enable Interactive Filtering
